OpenCodeX
=========

OpenCodeX is an independent, unofficial fork of OpenCode.

Upstream project
----------------
Name: OpenCode
Repository: https://github.com/anomalyco/opencode
License: MIT License (see LICENSE)

This repository contains code originally from OpenCode and modifications
made for the OpenCodeX product (desktop IDE shell, CLI branding, and
related tooling).

